article_id:228,category_name:News,title_name:Issue with Dragonyule Cleo's "Starlit Gift" Skill Description,image_path:,message:<div>There was an issue in Dragonyule Cleo&#39;s &quot;Starlit Gift&quot; skill description mentioning an increase in strength and critical rate during Phase II and Phase III.</div><div><br></div><div>The description was corrected as follows.</div><div>Before: &quot;Phase II increases the entire team&#39;s strength&quot;</div><div>After: &quot;Phase II increases the strength of the user and nearby allies&quot;</div><div><br></div><div>The skill&#39;s actual effects have not been modified.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1548913800,update_time1548913830